<template></template>

<script>
//import { ref } from "vue";
import { computed } from "vue";
import { useStore } from "vuex";
export default {
  name: "SingleProduct",
  components: {},
  setup() {
    const store = useStore();
    store.dispatch("getProductById");

    return {
      product: computed(() => store.getters.product),
    };
  },
};
</script>

<style></style>
